            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://twitter.com/WalkerBragman/status/1124442782322647040?s=20",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " of the Senate professing his desire to freeze all federal spending including Medicare, Medicaid, Social Security, and veterans’ benefits. Democratic voters today overwhelmingly support major government programs like Medicare-for-all and the Green New Deal -- two policies Kennedy has aligned himself with for his Senate run.",
            "type": "text",
